#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:55
#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:76
msgid ""
"Nozzle may be blocked when the temperature is out of recommanded range.\n"
"Please make sure whether to use the temperature to print"
msgstr ""
"当喷嘴温度高于推荐温度范围，打印时可能会发生堵塞。\n"
"请确认是否使用该温度打印"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:100
msgid ""
"Bed temperature of other layer is lower too much than bed temperature of "
"initial layer. \n"
"This may cause model broken free from build plate during printing. \n"
"Please check the bed temperature and make sure whether to use the value"
msgstr ""
"其它层热床温度比首层热床温度低太多。\n"
"这可能导致打印中模型从构建板脱落。\n"
"请检查热床温度并确认是否用相应数值"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:124
msgid ""
"Too small layer height.\n"
"Reset to 0.2"
msgstr "层高过小。将重置为0.2"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:137
msgid ""
"Too large layer height.\n"
"Reset to 0.2"
msgstr "层高过大。将重置为0.2"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:150
msgid ""
"Too small ironing spacing.\n"
"Reset to 0.1"
msgstr "熨烫线距过小。将重置为0.1"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:162
msgid ""
"Zero initial layer height is invalid.\n"
"\n"
"The first layer height will be reset to 0.2."
msgstr ""
"首层层高为无效的0值。\n"
"将被重置为0.2。"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:182
msgid ""
"Spiral mode only works when wall loops is 1, \n"
"support is disabled, top shell layers is 0 and sparse infill density is 0\n"
msgstr ""
"旋转模式只能在外墙层数为1，关闭支撑，顶层层数为0，稀疏填充密度为0时有效。\n"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:185
msgid ""
"Change these settings automatically? \n"
"Yes - Change these settings and enable spiral mode automatically\n"
"No  - Give up using spiral mode this time"
msgstr ""
"自动调整这些设置？\n"
"是 - 自动调整这些设置并开启旋转模式\n"
"否 - 暂不使用旋转模式"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:223
msgid ""
"Prime tower does not work when Adaptive Layer Height or Independent Support "
"Layer Height is on.\n"
"Which do you want to keep?\n"
"YES - Keep Prime Tower\n"
"NO  - Keep Adaptive Layer Height and Independent Support Layer Height"
msgstr ""
"擦拭塔不支持和自适应层高或支撑独立层高。同时开启\n"
"如何选择？\n"
"是 - 选择开启擦拭塔\n"
"否 - 选择保留自适应层高或支撑独立层高"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:229
msgid ""
"Prime tower does not work when Adaptive Layer Height is on.\n"
"Which do you want to keep?\n"
"YES - Keep Prime Tower\n"
"NO  - Keep Adaptive Layer Height"
msgstr ""
"擦拭塔不支持和自适应层高同时开启。\n"
"如何选择？\n"
"是 - 选择开启擦拭塔\n"
"否 - 选择保留自适应层高"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:235
msgid ""
"Prime tower does not work when Independent Support Layer Height is on.\n"
"Which do you want to keep?\n"
"YES - Keep Prime Tower\n"
"NO  - Keep Independent Support Layer Height"
msgstr ""
"擦拭塔不支持和支撑独立层高同时开启。\n"
"如何选择？\n"
"是 - 选择开启擦拭塔\n"
"否 - 选择保留支撑独立层高"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:306
#, boost-format
msgid "%1% infill pattern doesn't support 100%% density."
msgstr "%1% 填充图案不支持 100%% 密度。"

#: src/slic3r/GUI/ConfigManipulation.cpp:309
msgid ""
"Switch to zig-zag pattern?\n"
"Yes - switch to zig-zag pattern automaticlly\n"
"No  - reset density to default non 100% value automaticlly\n"
msgstr ""
"切换到锯齿图案？\n"
"是 - 自动切换到锯齿图案\n"
"否 - 自动重置为非100%填充密度\n"

